        <title>Creating a Boot Loader?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[@ollie123 Ollie123]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/u/ollie123">@ollie123</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>Remember the boot signature, after that you need to learn about int 13 and FAT to load your OS</p>
<p>[code=asm]bits 16<br>
org 0x7c00</p>
<p>start:<br>
cli<br>
hlt</p>
<p>times 510 - ($ - $$)<br>
dw 0xaa55[/code]</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/t/creating-a-boot-loader/403077/2">Read full topic</a></p>
